1. Prerequisites
    - KDE4.x >= 4.2
    - kdelibs-dev
    - kdebase-dev
    - cmake
2. Get it running
    2.1. Kompilation
	tar xvfj virtual_hdd_led-0.4.tar.bz2
	cd virtual_hdd_led-0.4
	cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr .
	make
    2.2. Installation
	sudo make install
	exit
    2.3. Plasma desktop restart
	killall plasma-desktop
	plasma-desktop
    2.4. Add virtual_hdd_led to the panel/desktop
	click on cashew - add applets - search hdd - drag it to desktop or double click on it to get in panel

3. Have fun
